programme.desc: In CNBC Documentaries’ “Generation Gamble,” CNBC’s Melissa Lee takes viewers on a journey to the intersection of online betting, trading and gaming – all of which surged in popularity and profits during the pandemic. As the smartphone generation comes of age, it’s overturning traditional concepts of money and risk and shaking up the markets.
